Package it.polimi.ingsw.generics

Class Visualizable

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.generics.Visualizable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Visualizable
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Utility class used to convert generic elements into images. It implements serializable because it's purpose is to support the objects sent from the server to the client (that are eventually going to be displayed to the user).
